    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but honestly the side effects are making me feel kinda nauseous and gross. if the skin is already looking totally normal, isn't it kind of overkill to keep putting these chemicals in my body for another week? feels like if the bacteria are gone, the medicine is just doing more harm than good at this point. wouldn't it be fine to just wrap it up now?",
